oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Fisk University Choir program - 1948-04-04 - '#21 Copy #2'
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WSM broadcast of the Fisk University Choir, directed by John F. Ohl with organist Arthur R. Croley. Recorded at the Fisk Memorial Chapel on the Fisk University campus. WSM announcer is Ott Devine.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Fisk University Choir
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Theme -- Announcer opening statement (Ott Devine) -- In The River Of Jordan -- Ott Devine talks -- Give To Jehovah -- Ott Devine talks -- Thou Know'st, Lord, The Secrets Of Our Hearts -- Ott Devine talks -- He Is King Of Kings -- Announcer closing statement (Ott Devine) -- Theme
